text: bagenyachiḫwachewimi sifira hulu gideluwachewi፡፡ ke’āwet’wachihumi sifira āwit’wachewi፡፡ mekerami kemegideli yibelit’i yeberetachi nati፡፡ betekeberewi mesigīdimi zenidi berisu wisit’i isikemīgadeluwachihu diresi ātigadeluwachewi፡፡ bīgadeluwachihumi gideluwachewi፤ yekeḥadīwochi k’it’ati inidezīhi newi፡፡
